<h1 id=3D"capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-2.Endpointsoverv=
iew">2. Endpoints overview</h1>
<p><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark"><strong><style type=3D"text/css">=
/*<![CDATA[*/
