gements/transactions">POST /arrangements/transactions</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-POST/arran=
gements/arrangementId/transactions/transactionId">POST /arrangements/arrang=
ementId/transactions/transactionId</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-POST/arran=
gements/accountId/consolidatedView">POST /arrangements/accountId/consolidat=
edView</a></li>
</ul></strong>
