<h2 id=3D"capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-POST/arrangement=
s/arrangementId/transactions/transactionId"><span>POST /arrangements/arrang=
ementId/transactions/transactionId&nbsp;</span></h2>
<p>This endpoint a detailed view of a transaction for the provided account =
ID and transaction ID in the request.</p>
<h3 id=3D"capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-5.1.Request">5.1=
. Request</h3>
<p>Header Parameters</p>
