<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(59,65,81);">x-appCorrelationId</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span><span class=3D"emoji-common-main-styles emoji-common-node   emoji-=
common-emoji-image   css-19bdfyn" title=3D":white_check_mark:">:tick:</span=
></span></p>
</div></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Must be a GUID (Globally unique message ident=
ifier). Consumer generated message identifier for correlation purposes. e.g=
. This is used to group together a number of downstream API/provider calls =
initiated from a single API call, comprising a business transaction. This M=
UST be propagated</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(59,65,81);">x-organisationId</span></td>
