common-emoji-image   css-19bdfyn" title=3D":white_check_mark:">:tick:</span=
></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The originating c=
onsumption channel invoking the API (eg. Partner, Staff, Customer). Note th=
at an API consuming another API should pass the value supplied by the calli=
ng application. Further information regarding this header can be found at<s=
pan>&nbsp;</span><a href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/cbH-B" =
rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/cbH-B</a>.</p><p><=
em>Available values</em><span>&nbsp;</span>: Partner, Public, Staff, Custom=
er, Prospect, Other</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
