: rgb(59,65,81);">x-userId</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span><span class=3D"emoji-common-main-styles emoji-common-node   emoji-=
common-emoji-image   css-19bdfyn" title=3D":white_check_mark:">:tick:</span=
></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The unique identi=
fier for the user invoking the API (eg. Staff salary number, Customer CIS/G=
CIS key, Partner CIS/GCIS key or other identifier).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(59,65,81);">x-userIdScheme</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span><span class=3D"emoji-common-main-styles emoji-common-node   emoji-=
common-emoji-image   css-19bdfyn" title=3D":white_check_mark:">:tick:</span=
></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The scheme (type)=
 applicable for the user identifier of the consumer invoking the API.</p><p=
>Available values : StaffSalaryNumber, CustomerInternalId, CustomerNumber, =
SystemProcess, CorporateUserId, ProspectId</p></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><span style=3D"color=
: rgb(59,65,81);">x-originatingBSB</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span><span class=3D"emoji-common-main-styles emoji-common-node   emoji-=
common-emoji-image   css-19bdfyn" title=3D":white_check_mark:">:tick:</span=
></span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>Identifies the BS=
B from which this request originated. The format should be XXY-ZZZ. The fir=
st two digits (XX) specify the bank or financial institution. The third dig=
it (Y) tells which state the branch is located in. The last three digits (Z=
ZZ) specify the address of the branch.</p></td>
</tr>
