</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;" class=3D"confluenceTd"><p>The Brand Silo th=
e caller is operating in. Brand Silo is a concept used in Westpac to segreg=
ate Customer records based on a combination of the organisation that =E2=80=
=9Cowns=E2=80=9D the customer relationship and the systems environment in w=
hich their identity records are created and maintained. A Brand Silo is a c=
lassification whereas a Brand is a descriptive entity associated with an Or=
ganisation.</p><p>Available values : WPAC, SGBBSA, BTPL</p></td>
