<h1 id=3D"capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-7.CoreSystemRout=
ing">7. Core System Routing</h1>
<p>The details of how CCMP Arrangement CAP API performs the routing can be =
found here: <strong><a class=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.co=
m.au/x/uylbWQ" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/uyl=
bWQ</a></strong></p>
<h1 id=3D"capprodsvcadmproddealacctadminstlarrngmntsvcngv1-8.Mapping">8. Ma=
pping</h1>
<p>The CCMP Arrangement CAP API mapping to its source systems can be found =
here: <strong><a class=3D"" href=3D"https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x=
/R2jeW" rel=3D"nofollow">https://confluence.srv.westpac.com.au/x/R2jeW</a><=
/strong></p>
